{
  "stem": "1873.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 301.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Please, I went-- I want out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't know what I was saying, because the door opened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was beaten up, but of I was taken out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He beat me, the guard was [? still ?] take me and took me to another cell where Zellinger was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It looked like Zellinger bribed them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] And it was maybe more people than down, than where I was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But it was clean.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there was a lot of food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I remember the first jail was a Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He wasn't a Jew, a Ukrainian peasant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was, they caught him hiding Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I remember he was sitting and praying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He crossed himself all the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So probably he was killed in [INAUDIBLE] together with Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And over there in this cell where I was now, was the more intellectuals, which were able to bribe the guards, because business was going on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I remember they put with a rope, they put down a basket with money through the-- through the-- through the bars.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And in turn, they pulled up food, bread, sausage for the Polish prisoners, they'd give in exchange.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "In the evening, there was some poetry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They did read poetry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was-- they were intellectuals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the atmosphere was much better.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we were forced every day to take down our shirts and do delousing, look for insects.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] One day, a-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a prisoner did get a piece of bread from-- from the home, from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So he told me, [INAUDIBLE], I will pick you up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And you put it-- there was a oven there-- put the bread in the oven on top.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he picked me up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I put away the bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
